<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.9.7">
<l>cēruṅ koṭaipuka ḻellaiyi lāṉaiyō rāyiram</l>
<l>pēru muṭaiya pirāṉaiyal lāṉmaṟ ṟiyāṉkilēṉ</l>
<l>māri yaṉaiyakai mālvarai yokkuntiṇ ṭōḷeṉṟu</l>
<l>pārilōr paṟṟaiyaip paccaip pacumpoykaḷ pēcavē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Except for the lord who possesses on thousand names,</l>
<l>who is without boundary for the fame of giving when one joins him, I cannot</l>
<l>tell lies green with freshness about a low person on earth,</l>
<l>saying “hands that resemble rain showers, firm shoulder similar to large mountain.”</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
